title: David Driessen
text:
David Driessen (born 24 November 1994) is a Dutch <a href="association%20football">football</a> player.
Club career.
He made his professional debut in the <a href="Eerste%20Divisie">Eerste Divisie</a> for <a href="Achilles%20%2729">Achilles '29</a> on 13 January 2017 in a game against <a href="Fortuna%20Sittard">Fortuna Sittard</a>.
